帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 LEMFRECK 荣获 2024 年威尔士音乐奖https://www.nme.com/news/music/lemfreck-crowned-winner-of-welsh-music-prize-2024-3801125?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lemfreck-crowned-winner-of-welsh-music- 2024年奖Liberty DunworthWed, 09 Oct 2024 13:26:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieMercury PrizePopRapRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3801125 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他击败了 Aleighcia Scott、Skindred、Gruff Rhys 等人的竞争</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lemfreck-crowned-winner-of-welsh-music-prize-2024-3801125">LEMFRECK 荣获 2024 年威尔士音乐奖的得主</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck-award@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> LEMFRECK 荣获 2024 年威尔士音乐奖。</p><p>昨晚（10 月 8 日），作为第 14 届年度颁奖典礼的一部分，主持人 Siân Eleri 为这位创作型歌手颁发了该奖项。这是为了庆祝这位地下说唱歌手去年发行的《Blood, Sweat &amp; Fears》专辑。</p><p> LEMFRECK 不仅被评为这一享有盛誉的奖项的获得者（该奖项授予他去年在威尔士或全世界威尔士人制作的最佳专辑），这次胜利还让 LMFRECK 获得了 10,000 英镑的奖金。</p><p>为了确保胜利，这位说唱歌手击败了雷鬼艺术家阿莱西亚·斯科特 (Aleighcia Scott) 的《Windrush Baby》专辑、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gruff-rhys">粗鲁·里斯 (Gruff Rhys</a> ) 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gruff-rhys-unveils-details-of-new-album-sadness-sets-me-free-3509407">《悲伤让我自由》(Sadness Sets Me Free)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skindred">斯金德雷 (Skindred</a> ) 的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skindred-announce-smile-again-uk-2024-autumn-tour-3757106">微笑</a>》(Smile) 专辑等激烈竞争。他们在英国专辑排行榜上排名第二，并荣获<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mobos-2024-check-out-all-the-winners-3584040">2024 年 MOBO 奖</a>最佳另类表演奖。</p><p> “感谢我的妈妈和爸爸——作为一个年轻的黑人孩子，他们不断地告诉我，我可以做任何事情，成为任何人，”伦弗里克在卡迪夫千禧中心接受奖项时说道。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：血、汗水和恐惧" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/03qQkP76LR2nxQExADuRbO?si=DeoUB9ZyRPm29J_pVesSqw&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p> “这个是去我在纽波特的社区的。如果我没有看到 Benji [Skindred 的 Webbe] 首先做这件事，我现在告诉你，我将无法做到这一点，所以我要感谢他，”他补充道。 “我想谈谈代表性是多么重要……当像我这样的艺术家赢得这样的奖项时，这不是一个小勾号——而是对艺术的确认。”</p><p>当晚的其他地方，嘻哈先驱 Eric Martin 和 DJ Jaffa 还因其对威尔士音乐界的贡献而获得了威尔士音乐灵感奖，Aleighcia Scott、Gruff Rhys、CHROMA、HMS Morris 和 LEMFREC K 进行了现场表演。</p><p> “热烈祝贺 LMFRECK 荣获 2024 年威尔士音乐奖。《Blood, Sweat &amp; Fears》是一张令人惊叹的专辑，评委们称赞它的远见和雄心。入围名单中的每张专辑都是独一无二的，我们希望该奖项能够让我们的音乐家们看到这些令人惊叹的作品，”2011 年威尔士音乐奖的联合创始人休·斯蒂芬斯 (Huw Stephens) 说道。</p><p> 2024 年颁奖典礼也标志着莱斯音乐节作为卡迪夫音乐城音乐节一部分的首次活动。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/welsh-music-prize-2023-winner-announced-3513093">去年的威尔士音乐奖由流行二人组 Rogue Jones（由 Ynyr Ifan 和 Bethan Mai 组成）及其第二张专辑《Dos Bebés》夺得</a></p><figure id="attachment_3801137" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3801137" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3801137" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck@2000x1270.jpg" alt="L E M F R E C K 荣获 2024 年威尔士音乐奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lemfreck@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3801137" class="wp-caption-text"> LEMFRECK 荣获 2024 年威尔士音乐奖。图片来源：威尔士音乐奖</figcaption></figure><p>昨晚，2024 年威尔士音乐奖颁奖典礼上举行了威尔士才华横溢的庆祝活动，此前，今年著名的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">水星奖</a>于 9 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2024-shortlist-to-be-revealed-live-final-ceremony-scrapped-3776857">在 Abbey Road Studios 举行</a>。</p><p>今年的奖项提名有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">《Charli XCX》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">《CMAT》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ghetts">《Ghetts》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">《最后的晚宴》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corinne-bailey-rae">《Corinne Bailey Rae》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beth-gibbons">《Beth Gibbons》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-cant-swim">《Barry Can&#39;t Swim》</a>等。</p><p>该奖项最终<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/english-teacher-win-the-2024-mercury-prize-for-this-could-be-texas-3791098">颁发给了正在崛起的利兹乐队 English Teacher，</a>他们的首张专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/english-teacher-this-could-be-texas-debut-album-review-tracklist-radar-3600231">This Could Be Texas</a> ”广受好评。凭借这一胜利，他们成为十年来第一个来自伦敦以外的地区获得该奖项的乐队。</p><p>在红地毯上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/english-teacher-to-continue-to-be-honest-about-artists-struggles-after-mercury-prize-win-3791255"><em>《NME》</em>在成员获胜后不久就与他们进行了交谈，他们解释说，他们希望“继续诚实地”讲述他们作为乐队的挣扎</a>。</p><p> “‘我们将成为这样做的乐队之一’从来都不是一个有意识的[选择]，”主唱莉莉·方丹解释道。 “只是当我们被问到有关这些事情的问题时，我们总是会诚实。如果我们继续陷入被问到这个问题的境地，我们将继续诚实地面对它。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_k5snVycZU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.1